snippet.title: Boreal Blade - Full Game Upgrade (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Boreal Blade is out today on Nintendo Switch with a free demo!
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/boreal-blade-switch/

The demo and full game are compatible, allowing players of both versions play together! In this video you can see some of the cool things you get by purchasing the full game.

Official Website: https://www.borealblade.com
Twitter:https://www.twitter.com/borealblade
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/borealblade
